1
00:00:13,990 --> 00:00:15,860
我们这就叫自由集会
This is what the freedom to assemble looks like!

2
00:00:16,220 --> 00:00:18,120
停止操纵媒体
Stop silencing the press!

3
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:20,670
停止迫害异己
Stop persecuting the opposition!

4
00:00:20,740 --> 00:00:24,100
停止关押同性恋人士
Stop imprisoning people simply because they're gay!

5
00:00:24,130 --> 00:00:26,230
你是在毁掉俄罗斯的未来
You're destroying Russia's future!

6
00:00:26,540 --> 00:00:27,810
佩特罗夫的车队来了之后
When Petrov's motorcade arrives,

7
00:00:27,810 --> 00:00:30,010
让军乐队使劲大声演奏
have the band already playing as loud as they can.

8
00:00:30,010 --> 00:00:31,220
我跟上校说一下
I'll speak to the Colonel.

9
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:33,530
-暴动小猫的姑娘呢  -我亲自跟她们交待了
- What about the Pussy Riot girls? - I briefed them myself.

10
00:00:33,530 --> 00:00:35,710
她们希望你跟佩特罗夫谈这些问题
Here's a list of the issues they want you to discuss with Petrov.

11
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:37,290
-一切就绪了  -告诉她们我谈了
- We're good to go. - Tell them I did.

12
00:00:37,290 --> 00:00:39,080
请她们共进晚餐真的好吗
Sure it's a good idea to have them at the dinner?

13
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:40,500
多聪明  她们是异见分子
It's a smart idea. They're dissidents.

14
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:42,270
肯定会让佩特罗夫头疼
They've been nothing but a pain in Petrov's ass.

15
00:00:42,270 --> 00:00:44,200
他想拍张照就收买她们吗  可以啊
He wants to co-opt them with a photo? Fine.

16
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:46,150
对他重要的  对我也重要
If it's important to him, it's important to me.

17
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:47,920
-鲍勃  -总统先生
- Bob. - Mr. President.

18
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,940
得尽快把修正案敲定好
We have to get these amendments out of committee.

19
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,690
把《美就法》递交国会
Get AmWorks on the floor.

20
00:00:51,690 --> 00:00:54,170
也许能通过一两个  七个不可能全过
We might be able to squeeze a couple through, but not all seven.

21
00:00:54,170 --> 00:00:55,510
那就调整资金来源
Then restructure the funding.

22
00:00:55,510 --> 00:00:57,460
一个委员会只递交一份修正案
Shoot for one amendment in one committee.

23
00:00:57,460 --> 00:00:58,490
找财政委员会试试
Try Ways and Means.

24
00:00:58,490 --> 00:01:00,550
一下子申请全款  共和党肯定不同意
The Republicans will never go for a lump sum.

25
00:01:00,550 --> 00:01:02,580
得根据各个委员会职责分割法案
We have to split it up into jurisdictional parts.

26
00:01:02,580 --> 00:01:04,080
我宣布《美国就业法案》时
When I announced America Works,

27
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:06,400
承诺了一千万就业岗位
I promised ten million jobs.

28
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:08,270
是不是该降低一下期望
Maybe it's time to lower expectations.

29
00:01:08,270 --> 00:01:09,240
-不行  听我...  -抱歉  先生
- No, look-- - Pardon me, sir.

30
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:11,570
佩特罗夫总统的车队还有15分钟到
President Petrov's motorcade is 15 out.

31
00:01:11,570 --> 00:01:13,100
-谢谢  -你去吧
- Thank you. - I'll let you go.

32
00:01:13,100 --> 00:01:15,170
鲍勃  还有几分钟  先坐下
Bob, we have a few more minutes. Please sit down.

33
00:01:15,170 --> 00:01:16,550
你今天的事够多了
You have a lot on your plate today.

34
00:01:16,550 --> 00:01:18,690
不如今晚的国宴上接着谈吧
Why don't we pick it up tonight at the state dinner?

35
00:01:19,030 --> 00:01:20,660
很期待呢  总统先生
Looking forward to it, Mr. President.

36
00:01:25,140 --> 00:01:26,870
懦夫的脸什么样
What is the face of a coward?

37
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:29,140
临阵脱逃了  只能看得见后脑勺
The back of his head as he runs from the battle.

38
00:01:51,730 --> 00:01:54,540
-欢迎  总统先生  -谢谢  总统先生
- Welcome, Mr. President. - Thank you, Mr. President.

39
00:01:55,010 --> 00:01:57,190
第一次来白宫吗
This is your first visit to the White House?

40
00:01:57,190 --> 00:02:00,500
是啊  但你是我经历过的第三任总统了
Yes, yes. But my third president.

41
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:11,190
我看过你对约旦河谷的提议了
I have reviewed your proposal for the Jordan Valley.

42
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:14,110
不错
Impressive.

43
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,890
你喜欢吗
So you liked the proposal?

44
00:02:19,330 --> 00:02:20,380
不行
The answer is no.

45
00:02:22,210 --> 00:02:23,860
我不是开玩笑  总统先生
It's not a joke, Mr. President.

46
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:27,920
我对你的计划没有任何兴趣
I have no interest whatsoever in pursuing your plan.

47
